			<description><![CDATA[<div class="story">
<div class="storyImg" style="width:600px;">
<div class="image"><a href="http://www.excite.co.jp/News/photo_news/p-8318860/" style="background-image:url(https://imgc.eximg.jp/i=https%253A%252F%252Fs.eximg.jp%252Fexnews%252Ffeed%252FExcite%252Fbit%252F2017%252FE1508920765519_7289_1.jpg,zoom=600,type=jpg);background-position:center center;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-size:cover;width:600px;height:447px;display:block"></a></div>
